People v. New York, N. H. & H. R. Co. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 14, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Chas. F. Tabor, Atty. Gen., for the People. Page & Taft, for defendant.

No opinion. Motion granted. See 5 N. Y. Supp. 945, 8 N. Y. Supp. 672.
